## Diagnostics

The four required-for-v0.1 diagnostics from
`factor_factory.diagnostics`:

1. `multi_index_assertions(panel)` — structural-integrity check.
2. `standardized_mean_differences(panel, ...)` — covariate balance.
3. `parallel_trends_plot(panel, ...)` — visual pre-trend check.
4. `residual_diagnostics(residuals, ...)` — Jarque-Bera + Shapiro-Wilk
   (+ Breusch-Pagan when `fitted_values=` is supplied).

See `DIAGNOSTICS_CHECKLIST.md` for the full diagnostics audit.

